sentence: Health  ministry  says  29  killed  in  Gaza  in  past  day.

article_title: Health ministry says 29 killed in Gaza in past day.
sentence: Before  the  school  strike  that  killed  nearly  two  dozen  people  was  reported,  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  in  Gaza  released  an  update  saying  29  people  had  been  killed  in  Gaza  in  the  last  24  hours  -  with  93  others  injured.
